HEADWORD: Retene
<hw>Ret"ene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/<?/<?/ pine
resin.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A white crystalline hydrocarbon,
polymeric with benzene. It is extracted from pine tar, and is also found
in certain fossil resins.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

